LogFile.FinalText: They look incredibly much like each other. That is what many people think about Denmark's two princesses. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie, but just as many - if not more - difrerences. They were both born abroad into genteel families and have each met their Prince of Denmark - Mary is married to crown prince Frederik and Marie to prince Joachim. Also their names and their looks are incredibly similar. Both are beautiful like models with long dark hair and big brown eyes. But in spite of their many similarities, Mary and Marie are also two individuals who have lived and are still living in their own ways, which has characterized their values and their individual character.
